{"head":{"title":"Pixar","subtitle":"Internship","date":"2011-09","layout":"Post","size":"small","image":"pixar.jpg","description":"Pixar Undergraduate Program Jessie Paint Building Explosion Created using Houdini's PyroFX and Pixar's in-house rigid body simulator. Theâ€¦"},"body":"<h1 id=\"pixar-undergraduate-program\"><a href=\"#pixar-undergraduate-program\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Pixar Undergraduate Program</h1>\n<h2 id=\"jessie-paint\"><a href=\"#jessie-paint\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Jessie Paint</h2>\n<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/32291161?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=ffffff\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitAllowFullScreen=\"true\" mozallowfullscreen =\"true\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"></iframe>\nOriginal scene was done using Maya particles that were processed in Houdini. This is my attempt at doing it using Houdini exclusively. Done at Pixar Animation Studios under mentorship of FX Technical Director Matt Wong.\n<div class=\"spacer\" />\n<h2 id=\"building-explosion\"><a href=\"#building-explosion\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Building Explosion</h2>\n<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/32290566?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=ffffff\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitAllowFullScreen=\"true\" mozallowfullscreen =\"true\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"></iframe>\n<p>Created using Houdini's PyroFX and Pixar's in-house rigid body simulator.</p>\n<p>The up-res version had problems with the auto-resizing fluid container I had set up; the container did not resize fast enough (this was before pyroFX automatically resized in in Houdini 12). Did not have time to do a re-sim with the fixed resize setup.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://dl.dropbox.com/u/422520/Site%20Images/pixar/HiResSmoke03_AL.png\" title=\"Smoke\"><img src=\"http://dl.dropbox.com/u/422520/Site%20Images/pixar/HiResSmoke03_AL.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"Smoke\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"spacer\" />\n<h2 id=\"modeling-and-texturing\"><a href=\"#modeling-and-texturing\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Modeling and Texturing</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/76575517@N08/6884411938/\" title=\"Controller04 by alxlu, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm7.staticflickr.com/6053/6884411938_3ef21030b8.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"Controller04\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/76575517@N08/6884411960/\" title=\"Controller03 by alxlu, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7249/6884411960_25928c5b8a.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"Controller03\"></a>\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/76575517@N08/6884411996/\" title=\"Controller02 by alxlu, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7066/6884411996_9c22c12f6e.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"Controller02\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"spacer\" />\n<h2 id=\"lighting\"><a href=\"#lighting\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Lighting</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/76575517@N08/7030530885/\" title=\"Woody by alxlu, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7203/7030530885_c4e2e0687e.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"Woody\"></a>\n<p>Lighting Exercise: Relit Woody based on a reference image from another movie.</p></p>\n","__filename":"work/pixar.md","__url":"/work/pixar/","__resourceUrl":"/work/pixar/index.html","__dataUrl":"/work/pixar/index.html.aa9fbaf16deb4899be7fbd8cd7061230.json"}